column5: WELL FRIDAY HAS FINALLY GOT HERE!!! BEEN LOOKIN FOWARD TO THIS TRIP SINCE THE WIFE GOT IT FOR ME AS PART OF MY CHRISTMAS PRESENT!! OUT OF MY ELEMENT SO IT SHOULD BE AN ADVENTURE  LOL (I PACKED SOME FILLETS JUST INCASE I DONT CATCH ANYTHING  LOL)  HAVE A GOOD AND SAFE WEEKEND ALL hopefully i'll be back with pics lol
Good luck, have a safe trip!!
Have a great trip, see yah when you get back!!   dsn
Good luck!!! Be careful on the drive ok?  Want you in one piece for the report and pics when you get back.

CC, your taking fillets with you,  booo,   you could have cursed the whole trip...lol,     jokin although i was up on Nip a couple weekends ago and one guy with us brought a frozen lake trout to eat, we told him he cursed himself,  sure enough, i think he caught 5 fish or so...   good luck up there, have fun
